Organization_in_contract;

Organization_or_person_in_organization_assignment;

Organization_relationship;

Person;

Person_in_organization;

Person_in_organization_relationship;

Retention_period;

Time_interval_assignment;

Time_interval.

This capability provides the ability to represent information about physically realized parts, assembly structures of physically realized parts and results gained by testing physically realized parts of assemblies.

Physical_instance;

